          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1650386536679-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>diced chicken thigh </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>ground coriander</strong>, <strong>half </strong>the <strong>grated ginger </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Mix to combine</p><p>Add your <strong>cornflour </strong>to the bowl and give everything a good stir until the chicken is fully coated – this is your <strong>coated chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1650386559928-x200.jpg",
