          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1650386616364-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>crispy chicken </strong>with the <strong>Thai-style rice </strong>and the <strong>spicy peanut sauce </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, serve the peanut sauce in a little bowl for dipping!</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chilli rounds</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
